  The arctic cirlce is a cold and deselate place. It had been frozen in ice 
for 3 years. It had landed in a pod and got frozen in the artic waters. Out 
of final desperation the pod found a suitable form. A Polar Bear. The pod 
freed itself from the ice. The new predacon imerged. Lost for all these 
years. It walked slowly up to the only pred signal it could find. It found 
itself lost and sent out a comm. "Come in predacons. I am looking for my 
predacon bretheren." His name Polartron. His function...unknown.

--part1_93.607bf5d.27a22c73_boundary
